{"tid":564028,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國客不知煙花取消：港府應做好通知","createTime":"2018-02-17T13:51:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-17T16:40:07.000Z","uid":39464,"like":40,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"677253179892ebbe62ed0e7e92e9c1903888a06a","tid":564028,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T13:51:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180217/large/1518872070_f540.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180217%2Flarge%2F1518872070_f540.jpg&h=75947f51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n來自深圳的雷先生（左一）<br />\n<br />\n 為哀悼大埔車禍，港府取消原定今晚8時舉行的煙花匯演。有在文化中心等看煙花的深圳旅客指，對煙花取消不知情，認為港府應做好通知；有攝影發燒友則稱，是因煙花取消才到海旁拍照。<br />\n<br />\n尖沙嘴海旁是看煙花的最佳位置，雖然煙花取消，但海旁仍有大批旅客拍攝維港夜景。現場所見，海旁的圍欄張貼告示，以簡體字、繁體字及英文，提醒今晚的煙花匯演取消。至下午6時，有文化中心職員將鐵馬搬至文化中心樓梯前，上面亦有相同告示，但甚少人理會該告示。<br />\n<br />\n來自深圳的雷先生第一次帶同父母來港遊玩，更早於下午5時許便到文化中心樓梯霸位，「香港每年大年初二都有煙火，所以特意過來看一下，順便帶父母散一下心」。他續指，文化中心樓梯位置較正中，能清楚看到煙花，更帶同牛奶、餅乾等乾糧，當作今晚晚餐，但當得知煙花已取消，神情顯得失落，「我們主要是為了這場煙花表演，特意過來等的，要不我們已經回內地了」。他認為，港府應從更多的渠道通知旅客取消煙花匯演，以免旅客白行一趟，現會改去餐廳吃飯，再提早回深圳。<br />\n<br />\n山東旅客朱先生亦偕多名親友，坐在文化中心樓梯等看煙花匯演，更反問記者：「幾點鐘開始？」當記者告知煙花匯演取消，他表示失望，但明白取消原因是為了哀悼，故會先食晚飯，再到山頂看夜景。<br />\n<br />\n從事IT業的袁先生則帶同腳架等器材，到海旁拍攝相片，「我知道今日冇煙花影，但見個天有啲景，咪出嚟影。反而有煙花睇就唔會出嚟，太多人」。他說，取消煙花的做法是對大埔車禍遇難者的尊重，故不會覺得掃興。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180217/large/1518871446_ae2f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180217%2Flarge%2F1518871446_ae2f.jpg&h=7ad844c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n山東旅客朱先生。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180217/large/1518871532_5522.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180217%2Flarge%2F1518871532_5522.jpg&h=c6488aaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n從事IT業的袁先生。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180217/large/1518871528_638f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180217%2Flarge%2F1518871528_638f.jpg&h=b1a66c1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180217/large/1518872681_7ac5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180217%2Flarge%2F1518872681_7ac5.jpg&h=8b70c0dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180217/57845551\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180217%2F57845551&d=qUdZpBE2NivVg8UHMiDe6QEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=f3abf95d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180217%2F57845551&h=27ecfdaa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180217/57845551</a>"},{"pid":"bd709e96be3547442ba495064cc5db296ad4555b","tid":564028,"uid":23707,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T14:08:46.000Z","msg":"全香港都知啦屌你無腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fdce332df657efa6b08c62c881561d69f716038","tid":564028,"uid":46452,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T14:15:57.000Z","msg":"屌。係支狗出街前唔翻牆收 下風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eff5492c44d8557d511c71c11bbee9754a8b973","tid":564028,"uid":15358,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T14:16:33.000Z","msg":"大陸睇唔到香港新聞呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"740cf3604e02c259ebe26d27115eb5b76d249b5c","tid":564028,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB